 <span style="color:rgb(191, 134, 96);font-style:italic;">Fri, 7 Oct 2005 19:47:51, Justice, What about UI? </span>
	<div style="margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;display:block;">So, what do you do for user interface code (e.g., on a web application)?  I know that quite a bit of it can be decoupled, but not all of it...</div>
