 <span style="color:rgb(191, 134, 96);font-style:italic;">Fri, 2 Dec 2005 16:15:56, Bill Krueger, Managability of 1000's of test cases </span>
	<div style="margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;display:block;">With the pro's come the con's. In this case, there's having to deal with the potentially overwhelming number (1000's) of test cases. For the reasons they you propose they have worth for examples and documentation, the numbers seem to negate that.<br clear="none"/><br clear="none"/>That said, I do like your thoughts.</div>
</div>
